WEBVTT

00:00:13.770 --> 00:00:16.870
IN THE YEAR 2000 THE
BBC STARTED TO

00:00:16.870 --> 00:00:20.300
RECORD THE LIVES
OF OF 25 CHILDREN.

00:00:20.300 --> 00:00:23.330
THEIR FAMILIES COME FROM ALL
OVER THE UNITED KINGDOM

00:00:23.330 --> 00:00:26.300
AND ALL WALKS OF LIFE.

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:29.170
HOW WILL THEIR PARENTS
INFLUENCE THEIR LIVES?

00:00:29.170 --> 00:00:32.930
AND HOW WILL THEIR GENES AND
THEIR ENVIRONMENT COMBINE

00:00:32.930 --> 00:00:37.670
TO FORM THEIR PERSONALITY?

00:00:37.670 --> 00:00:41.470
THIS HUGE PROJECT WILL
LAST FOR TWENTY YEARS.

00:00:41.470 --> 00:00:44.430
FOLLOWING THESE
CHILDREN AS THEY GROW,

00:00:44.430 --> 00:00:52.170
TO FIND OUT WHAT
MAKES US WHO WE ARE.

00:00:59.830 --> 00:01:02.630
NOBODY'S PERFECT.

00:01:02.630 --> 00:01:04.100
OUCH.

00:01:04.100 --> 00:01:13.270
NEITHER ARE CHILDREN,
NOR THEIR PARENTS.

00:01:13.270 --> 00:01:16.000
MOM!

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:20.430
HOW SIX ARE STARTING TO FEEL
THE INFLUENCE OF A WIDER WORLD.

00:01:20.430 --> 00:01:22.900
HOW DO WE WORK OUT
WHAT'S RIGHT OR WRONG,

00:01:22.900 --> 00:01:28.670
GOOD OR BAD?

00:01:28.670 --> 00:01:30.930
&nbsp WHAT'S THE VERY WORST THING
&nbsp ANYONE CAN DO?

00:01:30.930 --> 00:01:34.530
STEALING PEOPLES'
BAGS AND PURSES.

00:01:34.530 --> 00:01:37.630
PAINT WINDOWS.

00:01:37.630 --> 00:01:38.930
ROB.

00:01:38.930 --> 00:01:43.570
KILL PEOPLE WITH GUNS.

00:01:43.570 --> 00:01:51.030
THE EXTREMES ARE ONE THING,
BUT WHAT ABOUT EVERYDAY LIFE?

00:01:51.030 --> 00:01:54.300
WHERE DO WE GET
OUR VALUES FROM?

00:01:54.300 --> 00:01:57.900
OUR PARENTS?

00:01:57.900 --> 00:01:59.600
OR SOMEWHERE ELSE?

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:01.500
&nbsp YOU HURT HIS
&nbsp MOUTH, WHAT DO YOU SAY?

00:02:01.500 --> 00:02:02.400
&nbsp SORRY.

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:03.870
WHO SETS THE RULES?

00:02:03.870 --> 00:02:04.770
DADDY.

00:02:04.770 --> 00:02:05.900
MOMMY.

00:02:05.900 --> 00:02:07.570
MOMMY AND DADDY.

00:02:07.570 --> 00:02:10.670
MY CLASS MAKES RULES.

00:02:10.670 --> 00:02:13.130
THE HEADMASTER.

00:02:13.130 --> 00:02:14.530
THEY WON'T YELL AT ME.

00:02:14.530 --> 00:02:17.270
ME! ME! ME!

00:02:18.930 --> 00:02:22.430
SO WHICH RULES ARE PERMANENT
AND WHAT DO WE ACTUALLY BEND?

00:02:22.430 --> 00:02:24.800
WHAT VALUES DO WE WANT TO
PASS ON TO OUR CHILDREN

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:26.930
AND WHAT ARE THEY
ACTUALLY PICKING UP?

00:02:26.930 --> 00:02:34.000
AND IS THERE ANYTHING THAT
WE ALL STILL ALL BELIEVE IN?

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:37.100
TO BE CONFIDENT ABOUT
JUDGING RIGHT AND WRONG,

00:02:37.100 --> 00:02:41.800
YOU NEED TO HAVE LEARNED ONE OF
LIFE'S IMPORTANT LESSONS.

00:02:41.800 --> 00:02:46.170
WHICH IS WORSE - BREAKING
ONE GLASS ON PURPOSE

00:02:46.170 --> 00:02:50.670
OR SIX BY ACCIDENT?

00:02:56.670 --> 00:03:00.270
WHAT YOU MEAN TO
DO CAN MATTER.

00:03:00.270 --> 00:03:06.100
SOMETIMES MORE
THAN WHAT YOU ACTUALLY DO.

00:03:06.100 --> 00:03:07.730
CAUSE HE DID IT ON PURPOSE.

00:03:07.730 --> 00:03:08.870
ON PURPOSE.

00:03:08.870 --> 00:03:10.070
ON PURPOSE.

00:03:10.070 --> 00:03:11.930
HE MEANT TO BRAKE SOMETHING.

00:03:11.930 --> 00:03:14.070
&nbspAND WHAT DO YOU THINK
 &nbspHIS PUNISHMENT SHOULD BEE?

00:03:14.070 --> 00:03:15.530
GROUNDED.

00:03:15.530 --> 00:03:16.370
&nbspFOR HOW LONG??

00:03:16.370 --> 00:03:18.430
FOR 600 WEEKS.

00:03:18.430 --> 00:03:20.900
SOME ARE LATER TO
GRASP THIS THAN OTHERS.

00:03:20.900 --> 00:03:26.270
BUT HE DROPPED MORE
GLASSES THAN THE OTHER ONE.

00:03:26.270 --> 00:03:29.130
THIS NEW INSIGHT MEANS
OUR CHILDREN ARE WATCHING

00:03:29.130 --> 00:03:31.400
THE ADULTS AROUND THEM
TO LEARN HOW THEY

00:03:31.400 --> 00:03:36.330
SHOULD LIVE THEIR LIVES.

00:03:36.330 --> 00:03:40.930
AND THEY'RE SEEING SOME
VERY DIFFERENT LESSONS.

00:03:40.930 --> 00:03:47.470
ALONG THE THAMES ESTUARY ON
THE EDGE OF LONDON IS ERITH.

00:03:47.470 --> 00:03:50.870
IT'S IN THE LOWEST 20 PERCENT
OF DEPRIVED WARDS IN ENGLAND.

00:03:50.870 --> 00:03:52.470
AND IT'S WHERE ONE
OF OUR CHILDREN

00:03:52.470 --> 00:03:55.230
HAS SPENT ALL HER LIFE.

00:03:56.230 --> 00:04:02.170
I'M CHARLIE PLASTER!

00:04:02.170 --> 00:04:07.870
CHARLIE IS THE OLDEST
IN THE PLASTER FAMILY.

00:04:07.870 --> 00:04:12.470
THAT'S MOMMY, CAYLA AND DADDY.

00:04:12.470 --> 00:04:15.100
SHE LIVES WITH HER
MOM TONI, DAD ROB,

00:04:15.100 --> 00:04:19.170
SISTER CAYLA AND NEW
BABY BROTHER ALEX.

00:04:19.170 --> 00:04:21.630
LIKE ANY OTHER, THE
FAMILY HAS ITS RULES.

00:04:21.630 --> 00:04:24.030
DINNER IS TO BE AT THE TABLE.

00:04:24.030 --> 00:04:25.730
ALWAYS SAY
PLEASE AND THANK YOU.

00:04:25.730 --> 00:04:29.000
BEDTIME 7 O'CLOCK.

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:32.030
I'M NOT TELLING FIBS!

00:04:32.030 --> 00:04:35.770
ALTHOUGH CHARLIE DOESN'T
ALWAYS CHOOSE TO OBEY THEM.

00:04:35.770 --> 00:04:36.870
COME UPSTAIRS NOW!

00:04:36.870 --> 00:04:37.970
NO!

00:04:37.970 --> 00:04:43.100
ONE, TWO ,THREE!

00:04:43.100 --> 00:04:45.900
CHILDREN AND PARENTS DON'T
ALWAYS AGREE ON WHAT'S RIGHT

00:04:45.900 --> 00:04:49.270
AND WHAT'S WRONG.

00:04:49.270 --> 00:04:53.570
I'VE ALWAYS BIN TAUGHT
IF SOMEONE HITS YOU,

00:04:53.570 --> 00:04:54.400
YOU HIT THEM BACK.

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:56.030
AND MY MOM'S
ALWAYS GOING TO ME,

00:04:56.030 --> 00:04:57.770
IF YOU DON'T HIT THEM BACK,
I'LL DRIVE YOU UP THERE OR

00:04:57.770 --> 00:04:58.900
I'LL BEAT YOU MYSELF.

00:04:58.900 --> 00:05:00.730
SO I'M LIKE ALRIGHT GREAT.

00:05:00.730 --> 00:05:02.500
WHEN CHARLIE COMES HOME,

00:05:02.500 --> 00:05:04.270
SHE'S ALL SO AND SO'S
BEEN HORRIBLE TO ME

00:05:04.270 --> 00:05:06.530
AND I'M ALL WELL
JUST HIT HIM.

00:05:06.530 --> 00:05:07.800
HIT HIM BACK. I SAY TO HER.

00:05:07.800 --> 00:05:09.900
SHE'S LIKE NO BECAUSE I'LL GET
IN TROUBLE BY THE TEACHER

00:05:09.900 --> 00:05:14.170
AND I'M LIKE WELL YOU TELL
THE TEACHER YOUR MOM SAID

00:05:14.170 --> 00:05:15.770
HIT HIM BACK IF THEY
HURT ME.

00:05:15.770 --> 00:05:17.670
AND SHE'S LIKE NO,
IT'S WRONG.

00:05:17.670 --> 00:05:19.770
I'LL GET IN TROUBLE.

00:05:19.770 --> 00:05:23.030
WHEN TONI WAS A CHILD,
SHE WAS ALWAYS IN TROUBLE.

00:05:23.030 --> 00:05:25.200
WHEN SHE GOT
PREGNANT AT 16,

00:05:25.200 --> 00:05:28.770
IT CAME AS NO
SURPRISE TO HER MOM.

00:05:28.770 --> 00:05:31.070
SHE WAS A BIT OF A
BOISTEROUS CHILD,

00:05:31.070 --> 00:05:34.930
BEING EXCLUDED FROM SCHOOL AND
WHENEVER THERE WAS A FIRE

00:05:34.930 --> 00:05:37.100
OR ANYTHING SHE WAS
THERE IN THE FRONT,

00:05:37.100 --> 00:05:40.370
EVEN THOUGH SHE HAD
NOTHING TO DO WITH IT.

00:05:40.370 --> 00:05:44.830
I JUST LOVED THE ACTION.

00:05:44.830 --> 00:05:46.400
I SAID TO HER ONE DAY
YOU'RE GOING TO GROW UP

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:48.800
AND HAVE A CHILD
JUST LIKE YOURSELF.

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:51.470
MY MOM WAS TOLD THAT
AND SHE WAS CURSED

00:05:51.470 --> 00:05:53.700
BY MY GREAT GRANDMOTHER.

00:05:53.700 --> 00:05:56.100
THE GYPSY CURSE CAUSE
SHE WAS A GYPSY .

00:05:56.100 --> 00:06:00.500
AND SHE CURSED HER WITH GIRLS
AND HER GIRLS WITH GIRLS AND

00:06:00.500 --> 00:06:03.000
HER GIRLS WITH GIRLS AND
THEY'D ALL BE LIKE YOU.

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:05.830
AND PERHAPS I'VE CARRIED IT ON
BY WISHING THE SAME ON TONI.

00:06:05.830 --> 00:06:07.630
WHO KNOWS?

00:06:07.630 --> 00:06:11.730
ONLY TIME WILL TELL.

00:06:11.730 --> 00:06:15.200
CURSED OR OTHERWISE,
TONI ASSISTED BY HER MOM

00:06:15.200 --> 00:06:18.000
AND GRANDMOTHER, GAVE
BIRTH TO CHARLIE.

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:20.500
CHARLIE'S DAD
WASN'T ON THE SCENE.

00:06:20.500 --> 00:06:22.870
BUT THEN SHE GOT TOGETHER
WITH AN OLD FRIEND

00:06:22.870 --> 00:06:27.870
AND TONI'S LIFE TOOK
A NEW DIRECTION.

00:06:27.870 --> 00:06:30.500
THEY HAD TWO MORE
CHILDREN TOGETHER.

00:06:30.500 --> 00:06:33.800
AND TWO YEARS AGO, BOUGHT
THEIR FIRST FAMILY HOME.

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:39.030
COMPLETE WITH THE
FIRST FAMILY PET, NEO.

00:06:39.030 --> 00:06:40.670
AND IT'S NEO WHO'S NOW
PROVIDING CHARLIE

00:06:40.670 --> 00:06:43.700
WITH A POWERFUL LESSON
IN RIGHT AND WRONG.

00:06:43.700 --> 00:06:47.900
HE'S BEEN DOGNAPPED.

00:06:55.170 --> 00:06:57.370
&nbsp WHO'S KEEPING NEO?

00:06:57.370 --> 00:07:03.430
A OLD MAN WHO PICKED HIM UP
FROM OUR GARDEN AROUND THERE.

00:07:03.430 --> 00:07:04.870
&nbspDO YOU KNOW WHO TOOK HIM?

00:07:04.870 --> 00:07:06.970
NO.

00:07:06.970 --> 00:07:10.900
HE WAS SITTING ABOUT HERE AND
SOMEONE OBVIOUSLY BENT OVER

00:07:10.900 --> 00:07:15.400
THE FENCE BECAUSE
ALL THIS IS BROKEN.

00:07:15.400 --> 00:07:17.900
I WOULD HAVE RATHER SOMEONE
COME IN THE HOUSE,

00:07:17.900 --> 00:07:20.030
TAKEN EVERY BIT OF
GOLD I HAD.

00:07:20.030 --> 00:07:22.770
YOU KNOW THE TELE, ANYTHING.

00:07:22.770 --> 00:07:25.130
YOU KNOW, ABSOLUTELY ANYTHING.

00:07:25.130 --> 00:07:31.570
IT JUST GOT TO ME TO
THINK THEY GOT OUR DOG.

00:07:31.570 --> 00:07:33.000
&nbspIS YOUR MOMMY UPSETT?

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:34.830
SOMETIMES.

00:07:34.830 --> 00:07:37.130
&nbspHOW DO YOU KNOW WHEEN
 &nbspYOUR MOMMY'S UPSET?

00:07:37.130 --> 00:07:44.370
BECAUSE WHEN DADDY SHOUTS
AT HER, SHE CRIES.

00:07:48.270 --> 00:07:50.070
HELLO, SORRY TO
BOTHER YOU, I HAD MY DOG,

00:07:50.070 --> 00:07:52.300
I THINK HE WAS STOLEN...

00:07:52.300 --> 00:07:53.900
WHILE TONI GETS
ON THE PHONE,

00:07:53.900 --> 00:07:56.370
CHARLIE IS OUT
LOOKING FOR CLUES.

00:07:56.370 --> 00:07:59.400
I FOUND SOMETHING!

00:07:59.400 --> 00:08:03.400
IT'S GOING THAT WAY.

00:08:03.400 --> 00:08:04.300
&nbsp ANY SIGN?

00:08:04.300 --> 00:08:06.370
NO.

00:08:06.370 --> 00:08:08.430
WITH NO SIGN OF
NEO IN THE GARDEN,

00:08:08.430 --> 00:08:16.730
CHARLIE TAKES THE
SEARCH TO SCHOOL.

00:08:16.730 --> 00:08:20.200
CHARLIE'S TEACHER TURNS IT TO
A LESSON FOR THE WHOLE CLASS.

00:08:20.200 --> 00:08:22.200
&nbspOH, WHAT'S THIS?

00:08:22.200 --> 00:08:23.400
&nbspMY DOGGY.

00:08:23.400 --> 00:08:24.870
&nbspYOUR DOGGY.

00:08:24.870 --> 00:08:28.530
&nbspLETS HOPE THAT
&nbspYOU FIND HIM.

00:08:28.530 --> 00:08:30.470
&nbspIS HE A KIND DOG?

00:08:30.470 --> 00:08:32.030
&nbspYES?

00:08:32.030 --> 00:08:34.570
MORAL VALUES, CODES,
RULES, BOUNDARIES,

00:08:34.570 --> 00:08:36.630
THEY'RE EVERYWHERE IN SOCIETY.

00:08:36.630 --> 00:08:39.500
SO WE SET ASIDE THE RULES
THAT WE THINK ARE IMPORTANT

00:08:39.500 --> 00:08:42.730
AND THEN WE SORT OF
TRY AND ENFORCE THEM.

00:08:42.730 --> 00:08:45.230
BUT AT HOME THE MESSAGES
CHARLIE'S GETTING ARE LESS

00:08:45.230 --> 00:08:46.830
STRAIGHT FORWARD.

00:08:46.830 --> 00:08:51.470
BECAUSE I'M STILL
GROWING UP NOW,

00:08:51.470 --> 00:08:53.100
I CHANGE VIEWS EVERY
OTHER DAY SO IT'S HARD

00:08:53.100 --> 00:08:56.930
TO TRY AND SIT THERE AND SAY
THIS IS THIS AND THAT'S THAT,

00:08:56.930 --> 00:08:58.870
BECAUSE I MIGHT FEEL DIFFERENT.

00:08:58.870 --> 00:09:03.370
ALTHOUGH I'VE SAID TO
HER THIS IS WHAT YOU DO,

00:09:03.370 --> 00:09:07.470
SHE'S GOT HER OWN VIEWS AND
SHE'S GOT HER OWN MIND.

00:09:07.470 --> 00:09:14.800
AND SHE KNOWS SOMETIMES
I&nbsp AM WRONG YOU KNOW.

00:09:14.800 --> 00:09:17.970
OUTSIDE SCHOOL, CHARLIE'S
EXPERIENCE OF RIGHT AND WRONG

00:09:17.970 --> 00:09:21.100
IS FULL OF GREY AREAS.

00:09:21.100 --> 00:09:23.970
THAT NIGHT NEO TURNS
UP ON THE DOORSTEP

00:09:23.970 --> 00:09:26.470
WITH A STRANGER
DEMANDING CASH.

00:09:26.470 --> 00:09:30.570
THE NEXT DAY TONI IS STILL
UPSET ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED.

00:09:30.570 --> 00:09:32.030
SHE SAID IF THEY
GIVE OUR DOG BACK

00:09:32.030 --> 00:09:34.000
THEY WANT MONEY
FOR A NEW DOG.

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:36.070
SO ROB OFFERED HER
FIFTY POUNDS

00:09:36.070 --> 00:09:38.700
AND SHE TOOK IT LIKE
WITHOUT ANYTHING.

00:09:38.700 --> 00:09:42.430
BUT I SAID TO HIM IF I FOUND IT,
I WOULDN'T EXPECT A REWARD.

00:09:42.430 --> 00:09:46.430
I WOULD BE LIKE THERE'S YOUR
DOG. YOU'VE MISSED HIM.

00:09:46.430 --> 00:09:48.600
HAVE YOUR BACK SORT OF THING.

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:56.300
AND CHARLIE HAS SEEN FIRST
HAND THAT CRIME SOMETIMES PAYS.

00:09:56.300 --> 00:09:58.900
WHEN ROB SAID CAN
WE HAVE OUR DOG BACK?

00:09:58.900 --> 00:10:01.930
AND THEN SHE SAID UM,

00:10:01.930 --> 00:10:11.130
IF YOU WANT TO BUY
THIS DOG, PAY FOR IT.

00:10:11.130 --> 00:10:14.030
CHARLIE IS SEEING DIFFERENT
MODELS OF RIGHT AND WRONG

00:10:14.030 --> 00:10:16.330
AT HOME AND AT SCHOOL.

00:10:16.330 --> 00:10:19.230
SO WHAT'S SHE PICKING UP?

00:10:24.500 --> 00:10:27.130
AT NEARLY SIX WHAT DO
OUR CHILDREN KNOW ABOUT

00:10:27.130 --> 00:10:31.230
THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN
RIGHT AND WRONG?

00:10:31.230 --> 00:10:32.930
WE SET THEM A TEST.

00:10:32.930 --> 00:10:37.170
WHAT IS WORSE, LEAVING
YOUR ROOM UNTIDY,

00:10:37.170 --> 00:10:43.100
OR KICKING YOUR
FAMILY PET?

00:10:43.100 --> 00:10:45.070
THAT ONE.

00:10:46.400 --> 00:10:54.630
STEALING SWEETS OR
NOT SAYING THANK YOU?

00:10:54.630 --> 00:10:57.030
MOST OF THE CHILDREN KNEW
THAT KICKING OR STEALING

00:10:57.030 --> 00:10:59.130
WERE WORSE THAN
TALKING IN CLASS

00:10:59.130 --> 00:11:02.630
OR LEAVING YOUR
ROOM UNTIDY.

00:11:02.630 --> 00:11:05.700
SCIENTIST THINK THIS
ABILITY TO DISTINGUISH

00:11:05.700 --> 00:11:09.800
WHAT IS MORALLY WRONG FROM WHAT
IS MERELY A SOCIAL CONVENTION

00:11:09.800 --> 00:11:13.600
STARTS WHEN WE ARE
AS YOUNG AS 4.

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:16.270
WHAT ABOUT CHARLIE?

00:11:16.270 --> 00:11:17.570
&nbsp NATASHA NEVER SAYS THANK YOU.

00:11:17.570 --> 00:11:20.130
&nbsp GWEN STEALS HER FRIENDS TOY.

00:11:20.130 --> 00:11:22.070
&nbsp WHO'S THE NAUGHTIEST?

00:11:22.070 --> 00:11:23.400
&nbsp NATASHA?

00:11:23.400 --> 00:11:24.470
&nbsp WHY?

00:11:24.470 --> 00:11:28.100
BECAUSE SHE
DOESN'T SAY THANK YOU.

00:11:28.100 --> 00:11:29.400
&nbsp JOE?

00:11:29.400 --> 00:11:31.630
&nbsp WHY?

00:11:31.630 --> 00:11:33.800
CAUSE.

00:11:33.800 --> 00:11:36.770
OUT OF FIVE QUESTIONS
CHARLIE ONLY GOT IT RIGHT

00:11:36.770 --> 00:11:39.270
IN TWO CASES.

00:11:39.270 --> 00:11:41.130
SHE SEEMS TO FEEL THAT
MANNERS ARE MORE IMPORTANT

00:11:41.130 --> 00:11:44.770
THAN HITTING OR STEALING.

00:11:44.770 --> 00:11:48.800
BUT FOR ONE CHILD THERE
WAS ABSOLUTELY NO DOUBT.

00:11:48.800 --> 00:11:52.300
I THINK THAT ONE.

00:11:52.300 --> 00:11:53.530
&nbsp WHO DO YOU THINK
&nbsp IS THE NAUGHTIEST?

00:11:56.470 --> 00:11:57.770
&nbsp WHY?

00:11:57.770 --> 00:12:00.400
BECAUSE SHE KICKS.

00:12:00.400 --> 00:12:03.100
SO WHERE DID EVE LEARN
WITH SUCH CERTAINTY

00:12:03.100 --> 00:12:06.730
THE DISTINCTION BETWEEN
RIGHT AND WRONG?

00:12:09.430 --> 00:12:11.600
IT'S EASTER IN WORCESTERSHIRE.

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:14.400
EVE SCABOROUGH IS LEADING
HER CLASS UP TO CHURCH

00:12:14.400 --> 00:12:16.470
FOR THEIR EASTER SERVICE.

00:12:16.470 --> 00:12:20.170
BUT THERE'S
TEMPTATION IN THE WAY.

00:12:20.170 --> 00:12:22.730
THESE LOOK YUMMY DON'T THEY?

00:12:22.730 --> 00:12:26.930
I'M NOT TEMPTED TO EAT THESE,
BUT I AM TEMPTED TO EAT

00:12:26.930 --> 00:12:30.100
THAT ONE BUT NOT ALL THOSE
ONES, THE RED ONES.

00:12:30.100 --> 00:12:32.970
I AM TEMPTED TO EAT THOSE.

00:12:32.970 --> 00:12:37.530
BUT EVE KNOWS WHAT COULD
HAPPEN IF SHE DOESN'T RESIST.

00:12:37.530 --> 00:12:39.100
I MIGHT NOT GO TO HEAVEN

00:12:39.100 --> 00:12:42.670
I MIGHT GO TO THE OTHER
BAD PLACE INSTEAD.

00:12:42.670 --> 00:12:45.330
I MIGHT GO THERE.

00:12:45.330 --> 00:12:52.000
NOW WHAT DOES THIS MAKE YOU
THINK OF IN THE EASTER STORY?

00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:55.330
IT'S NOT JUST FROM
SCHOOL AND CHURCH

00:12:55.330 --> 00:12:57.400
THAT SHE'S PICKED
UP HER VALUES.

00:12:57.400 --> 00:13:00.430
MOM CAROLINE AND DAD TIM
BELIEVE THAT PRAYER

00:13:00.430 --> 00:13:04.470
CHANGES LIVES.

00:13:04.470 --> 00:13:08.470
SIX YEARS AGO THEY'D GIVEN
UP ALL HOPE OF HAVING A BABY.

00:13:08.470 --> 00:13:10.470
AND THEN CAME EVE.

00:13:10.470 --> 00:13:11.830
IT IS A MIRACLE.

00:13:11.830 --> 00:13:15.100
IT IS UNEXPLAINABLE.

00:13:15.100 --> 00:13:18.330
WHEN SHE WAS BORN IT WAS JUST
SUCH A HAPPY MOMENT YOU KNOW.

00:13:18.330 --> 00:13:20.800
I JUST KINDA FELT
LIKE A HERO

00:13:20.800 --> 00:13:24.470
AND I WAS SAUNTERING
ALONG YOU KNOW.

00:13:24.470 --> 00:13:28.500
BUT THEN TIM LOST HIS JOB AND
CAROLINE WENT THROUGH SEVERE

00:13:28.500 --> 00:13:30.870
POST NATAL DEPRESSION.

00:13:30.870 --> 00:13:32.500
PRAYER SAVED THEM AGAIN.

00:13:32.500 --> 00:13:36.230
AND THEN GAVE THEM THE
OPPORTUNITY TO WORK FOR GOD.

00:13:36.230 --> 00:13:38.930
THEY NOW MANAGE A
