AND SUDDENLY THERE IS
SOMEONE ELSE IN THE FAMILY

00:17:25.370 --> 00:17:27.730
TO WORRY ABOUT AS WELL.

00:17:27.730 --> 00:17:30.470
I WAS FEELING RATHER
ILL I THINK IN APRIL.

