EVE'S PARENTS' FAITH MAY
PREVENT THEM FROM WORRYING

00:18:33.970 --> 00:18:37.630
ABOUT DEATH BUT ALL THESE
PROBLEMS ARE GETTING TO EVE.

00:18:37.630 --> 00:18:39.900
YOU KNOW ABOUT
THE BABY?

