&nbsp BECAUSE?

00:20:04.300 --> 00:20:06.800
BECAUSE I'M AN ANGEL.

00:20:06.800 --> 00:20:08.270
&nbsp WHAT DOES GOD
&nbsp LOOK LIKE?

00:20:08.270 --> 00:20:11.500
HOPEFULLY SOMETHING ATTRACTIVE
AND EASY ON THE EYE.

00:20:11.500 --> 00:20:13.330
BECAUSE WE'RE GONNA BE
SPENDING ETERNITY WITH HIM

