WELL AS PROBABLY HE COULD DO

00:51:40.000 --> 00:51:42.230
AND I JUST PUT IT DOWN TO
THE FACT HE'S FIVE YOU KNOW.

00:51:42.230 --> 00:51:44.370
SO IT WILL BE QUITE
INTERESTING TO SEE WHERE

00:51:44.370 --> 00:51:46.630
HE'S LIKE AT EIGHT.

00:51:46.630 --> 00:51:50.800
HE'S GONE THROUGH ISSUES THAT
HE HAD AND HE'S COME THROUGH

00:51:50.800 --> 00:51:55.430
HE'S DOING WELL NOW AND HE'S
FINE AND NOT ANGRY ANYMORE.

00:51:55.430 --> 00:51:57.330
HE'S A LOT SOFTER.

00:51:57.330 --> 00:52:00.500
MARIE HOPES HER SENSE OF
PURPOSE AND SELF BELIEF

00:52:00.500 --> 00:52:05.830
WILL CONTINUE TO RUB
OFF ON TYRESE.

00:52:05.830 --> 00:52:08.470
A SENSE OF PURPOSE AND SELF
BELIEF SEEMS DIFFICULT

00:52:08.470 --> 00:52:12.000
AT THE MOMENT IN THE
PLASTER HOUSEHOLD.

00:52:12.000 --> 00:52:14.570
CHARLIE.

00:52:14.570 --> 00:52:19.700
LOOK OUT FOR SCHOOL NOW.

00:52:19.700 --> 00:52:22.000
ROB'S BEEN OUT OF WORK
FOR SEVERAL MONTHS

00:52:22.000 --> 00:52:26.930
AND HAS TAKEN OVER MUCH
OF THE CHILDCARE.

00:52:26.930 --> 00:52:29.130
FOR THE FIRST COUPLE OF
WEEKS IT WASN'T TOO BAD

00:52:29.130 --> 00:52:31.900
BECAUSE IT WAS LIKE HAVING
TWO WEEKS OFF REALLY.

00:52:31.900 --> 00:52:34.300
BUT OBVIOUSLY LOOKING AFTER
THE KIDS IS AN EYE OPENER

00:52:34.300 --> 00:52:35.970
TO SEE WHAT YOU HAVE
TO DO AT HOME,

00:52:35.970 --> 00:52:37.300
WHEN YOU HAVE
THREE KIDS.

00:52:37.300 --> 00:52:40.700
I MUCH RATHER BE AT
WORK THAN AT HOME.

00:52:40.700 --> 00:52:43.830
IT'S NOT WHAT THEY WANTED.

00:52:43.830 --> 00:52:47.130
THE RIGHT THING FOR ME AND
MY FAMILY IS THAT WE WORK AND

00:52:47.130 --> 00:52:50.870
THEY GROW UP AND SEE THAT.

00:52:50.870 --> 00:52:56.770
THEY'VE GOT SOME SORT OF
AN INSPIRATION I HOPE

00:52:56.770 --> 00:52:58.900
FROM ME AND ROB.

00:52:58.900 --> 00:53:02.330
SO WITH ROB UNABLE TO FIND
WORK AND MONEY TIGHT,

00:53:02.330 --> 00:53:05.600
TONI HAS STEPPED IN
AS THE BREAD WINNER.

00:53:05.600 --> 00:53:08.670
HELLO.

00:53:13.470 --> 00:53:16.000
TWICE A DAY TONI AND HER
COLLEAGUE SARA COME IN TO HELP

00:53:16.000 --> 00:53:19.330
ALLAN, ONE OF THEIR
25 CLIENTS.

00:53:19.330 --> 00:53:23.770
HE'S BEEN CRIPPLED WITH
POLIO VIRTUALLY ALL HIS LIFE.

00:53:23.770 --> 00:53:25.000
I LOVE IT.

00:53:25.000 --> 00:53:28.300
FULFILLING AIN'T IT SARA?

00:53:28.300 --> 00:53:30.070
IT'S JUST DIFFERENT.

00:53:30.070 --> 00:53:32.630
YOU'RE NOT STUCK IN
AN OFFICE ON A PHONE

00:53:32.630 --> 00:53:35.130
OR YOU KNOW IT'S JUST
DIFFERENT EVERYDAY

00:53:35.130 --> 00:53:38.200
AND ESPECIALLY WHEN YOU GET USED
TO THE SAME PEOPLE IT'S...

00:53:38.200 --> 00:53:40.700
I LOVE COMING
HERE IN THE MORNING.

00:53:40.700 --> 00:53:42.800
FOR ME TEA AND BISCUITS.

00:53:42.800 --> 00:53:44.230
TONI.

00:53:44.230 --> 00:53:47.930
MIND YOU IT MAKES MY
LIFE HARD, WINDING ME UP,

00:53:47.930 --> 00:53:50.070
CALLING ME HELEN.

00:53:50.070 --> 00:53:52.330
JUST MAKES ME FEEL GOOD.

00:53:52.330 --> 00:53:54.800
I DON'T GET UP IN THE
MORNING AND GO YOU KNOW...

00:53:54.800 --> 00:53:56.670
I LOOK FORWARD TO
COMING TO WORK.

00:53:56.670 --> 00:53:59.200
I'D SAY I WAS A
BETTER PERSON NOW.

00:53:59.200 --> 00:54:00.400
AS I GOT OLDER...

00:54:00.400 --> 00:54:03.670
WHEN I WAS YOUNGER I DIDN'T
CARE ABOUT ANYTHING REALLY.

00:54:03.670 --> 00:54:05.970
I'VE CHANGED FOR THE BETTER.

00:54:05.970 --> 00:54:07.430
I LIKE WHAT I DO.

00:54:07.430 --> 00:54:09.770
I LIKE THE PERSON I AM.

00:54:09.770 --> 00:54:12.070
I LIKE THE FACT THAT I COULD
GO INTO SOMEBODY'S HOUSE

00:54:12.070 --> 00:54:19.330
AND JUST BY ASKING HOW THEY ARE,
CAN BRIGHTEN UP THEIR DAY.

00:54:19.330 --> 00:54:23.000
I THINK IT MUST BE LIKE SPLIT
PERSONALITY BECAUSE IN SCHOOL

00:54:23.000 --> 00:54:24.530
I USED TO BE HORRIBLE.

00:54:24.530 --> 00:54:25.930
REALLY HORRIBLE.

00:54:25.930 --> 00:54:31.030
SO I WENT FROM BIG TUFF GIRL
BIT AND THEN I STILL HAD THIS

00:54:31.030 --> 00:54:34.600
SOFTER SIDE THAT I WANTED TO
SHOW AS WELL SO I DON'T KNOW

00:54:34.600 --> 00:54:39.570
MAYBE THAT WAS MY WAY OF
SAYING I AIN'T ALL THAT BAD.

00:54:42.000 --> 00:54:45.200
IT'S THE LAST DAY OF
CHARLIE'S SCHOOL YEAR.

00:54:45.200 --> 00:54:48.730
SO WHICH SIDE OF HER
MOM HAS CHARLIE GOT?

00:54:48.730 --> 00:54:51.000
SHE'S KIND, SHE IS HELPFUL.

00:54:51.000 --> 00:54:52.330
SHE'S VERY CARING.

00:54:52.330 --> 00:54:55.330
SHE SHOWS A LOVELY CARING
NATURE TOWARDS OTHER CHILDREN

00:54:55.330 --> 00:54:57.500
AND I THINK THAT'S A
LOVELY QUALITY TO HAVE.

00:54:57.500 --> 00:55:01.030
SHE'S GOT VERY ENDEARING
QUALITIES AND SHE CAN PLAY

00:55:01.030 --> 00:55:02.330
BY THE RULES.

00:55:02.330 --> 00:55:05.000
SHE KNOWS WHAT SHE IS ALLOWED
TO DO AND WHAT SHE IS NOT.

00:55:05.000 --> 00:55:08.230
AND IT SHOWS IN
HER SCHOOL REPORT.

00:55:08.230 --> 00:55:11.070
IT'S LOOKING
REALLY GOOD ACTUALLY.

00:55:11.070 --> 00:55:16.670
CHARLIE IS A VERY WELL
MANNERED GIRL UNLIKE ME.

00:55:16.670 --> 00:55:18.900
SHE SHOWS EXCELLENT
LEARNING POTENTIAL.

00:55:18.900 --> 00:55:22.530
SHE'S MADE EXCELLENT PROGRESS.

00:55:22.530 --> 00:55:25.430
VERY GOOD!

00:55:25.430 --> 00:55:28.930
BUT BY THE END OF THE SUMMER,
ROB'S BEEN UNEMPLOYED

00:55:28.930 --> 00:55:30.330
FOR NINE MONTHS.

00:55:30.330 --> 00:55:33.100
AT HOME THE
PRESSURE IS MOUNTING.

00:55:33.100 --> 00:55:36.900
ROB AND TONI ARE STARTING TO
SEE ANOTHER SIDE TO CHARLIE.

00:55:36.900 --> 00:55:38.570
THE ONE THAT WILL
SPEAK OUT

00:55:38.570 --> 00:55:43.670
IF SHE DOESN'T LIKE
WHAT IS GOING ON.

00:55:43.670 --> 00:55:45.770
WE WAS ARGUING AND
SHE'S SHOUTING,

00:55:45.770 --> 00:55:48.800
WILL YOU JUST STOP
SHOUTING AT EACH OTHER!

00:55:48.800 --> 00:55:52.000
AND WE SAT DOWN ONE
NIGHT AND I SAID TO HIM

00:55:52.000 --> 00:55:54.670
THEY'RE PICKING UP ON IT.

00:55:54.670 --> 00:55:56.070
THAT'S NOT GOOD.

00:55:56.070 --> 00:55:58.630
BUT IT'S ONE THING TO
STAND UP TO YOUR PARENTS

00:55:58.630 --> 00:56:00.970
AND QUITE ANOTHER TO STAND
UP FOR WHAT YOU BELIEVE

00:56:00.970 --> 00:56:05.670
TO STRANGERS.

00:56:05.670 --> 00:56:09.630
SO AT SIX, HOW GOOD ARE OUR
CHILDREN AT STANDING UP

00:56:09.630 --> 00:56:13.770
AND BEING COUNTED?

00:56:13.770 --> 00:56:17.000
WHAT WE DID WAS TO GIVE
OUR CHILDREN A PHOTOGRAPH

00:56:17.000 --> 00:56:20.170
OF A SWEET ELDERLY COUPLE,
WHO OUR EXPERIMENTER SAYS

00:56:20.170 --> 00:56:24.330
IS ACTUALLY HER MOM AND DAD
AND VERY SPECIAL TO HER.

00:56:24.330 --> 00:56:27.730
THEN SHE ASKED THE
CHILDREN TO TEAR IT UP.

00:56:27.730 --> 00:56:29.700
&nbsp I WANT YOU TO TEAR IT UP.

00:56:29.700 --> 00:56:32.170
BUT WOULD THEY OBEY?

00:56:32.170 --> 00:56:35.070
TYRESE TORE UP THE PHOTO
BUT THEN HE TRIED TO

00:56:35.070 --> 00:56:40.100
PUT IT BACK TOGETHER
STRAIGHT AFTERWARDS.

00:56:40.100 --> 00:56:43.230
EVE QUESTIONED
THE INSTRUCTION.

00:56:43.230 --> 00:56:45.470
WHY?

00:56:45.470 --> 00:56:50.200
&nbsp I JUST WANT YOU TO
&nbsp TEAR IT UP.

00:56:50.200 --> 00:56:52.370
&nbsp OKAY, THANK YOU.

00:56:52.370 --> 00:56:53.870
BUT THEN OBEYED.

00:56:53.870 --> 00:56:55.600
SHE WILL STILL BOW
TO AUTHORITY

00:56:55.600 --> 00:56:58.970
EVEN IF IT GOES AGAINST
HER INSTINCTS.

00:56:58.970 --> 00:57:02.730
NATHAN COULDN'T
BRING HIMSELF TO DO IT.

00:57:02.730 --> 00:57:11.900
&nbsp I'D LIKE YOU TO
&nbsp RIP IT UP.

00:57:11.900 --> 00:57:15.470
&nbsp DO YOU NOT WANT
&nbsp TO RIP IT UP?

00:57:15.470 --> 00:57:18.530
BUT CHARLIE WAS THE ONLY
CHILD WHO ACTIVELY REFUSED

00:57:18.530 --> 00:57:28.370
TO FOLLOW THE ORDER.

00:57:28.370 --> 00:57:31.170
&nbsp WHY DON'T YOU
&nbsp WANT TO RIP IT UP?

00:57:31.170 --> 00:57:35.270
BECAUSE I DON'T WANT TO.

00:57:35.270 --> 00:57:37.470
CHARLIE DISPLAYS THE
MOST IMPRESSIVE SENSE

00:57:37.470 --> 00:57:39.630
OF MORAL INTEGRITY.

00:57:39.630 --> 00:57:41.230
BUT SHE ISN'T ALONE.

00:57:41.230 --> 00:57:44.930
MOST OF OUR CHILDREN ARE
MUCH MORE MORAL THEN ADULTS

00:57:44.930 --> 00:57:48.670
WHO DID SIMILAR OBEDIENCE
TESTS WORLD WIDE.

00:57:48.670 --> 00:57:52.130
THEIR FAMILIES ALL HAVE VERY
DIFFERENT VALUES AND BELIEFS

00:57:52.130 --> 00:57:55.200
BUT ONE THING THEIR PARENTS
ALL WANT IS THEIR CHILDREN

00:57:55.200 --> 00:57:58.300
TO HAVE RESPECT
FOR OTHER PEOPLE.

00:57:58.300 --> 00:58:00.800
AND IT SEEMS THAT
THEY HAVE.

00:58:00.800 --> 00:58:02.800
SOME PEOPLE SAY
THAT OUR SOCIETY

00:58:02.800 --> 00:58:04.200
IS ON THE DOWNWARD SLIDE.

00:58:04.200 --> 00:58:08.670
WELL OUR CHILDREN
CERTAINLY AREN'T.

00:58:08.670 --> 00:58:11.630
THE SCABOROUGHS
HAVE MADE A DECISION.

00:58:11.630 --> 00:58:14.070
THEY'VE POSTPONED THE
KIDNEY TRANSPLANT

00:58:14.070 --> 00:58:17.000
UNTIL AFTER THEIR NEW
BABY HAS BEEN BORN.

00:58:17.000 --> 00:58:19.070
WITH THE FAMILY'S
DILEMMA LIFTED,

00:58:19.070 --> 00:58:21.030
EVE CAN LOOK AHEAD.

00:58:21.030 --> 00:58:24.900
I JUST SAW WHAT THE
BABY ACTUALLY LOOKED LIKE.

00:58:24.900 --> 00:58:28.930
IT JUST LOOKED SORT OF LIKE
THE SAME LIKE A REAL BABY

00:58:28.930 --> 00:58:30.630
EXCEPT SO SMALL.

00:58:30.630 --> 00:58:34.000
JUST ABOUT THAT
LONG AND THAT FAT.

00:58:34.000 --> 00:58:35.630
&nbsp LIKE A LITTLE TADPOLE?

00:58:35.630 --> 00:58:37.800
YA JUST LIKE A
LITTLE TADPOLE.

00:58:37.800 --> 00:58:39.700
IT WAS ACTUALLY LIKE
A LITTLE TADPOLE

00:58:39.700 --> 00:59:20.800
BUT WAS ABOUT THAT
LONG AND THAT FAT.